OUR BUSINESSES









Licensing The Licensing business is aligned around five strategic brand priorities: Disney Media, Classics & Entertainment, Disney & Pixar Animation, Disney Princess, Frozen & Tinker Bell, Lucasfilm and Marvel.
View More













Retail Disney Retail encompasses Disney Store Worldwide – which operates more than 330 stores and related ecommerce sites in North America, Europe and Asia – and Integrated Retail, which consolidates all North America retail channels into one seamless, integrated team across The Walt Disney Company.
View More













Games & Interactive Experiences The Disney Games & Interactive Experiences business is comprised of internally developed, licensed and co-developed mobile products, as well as licensed console video games. These leading, world-class experiences draw upon the most beloved stories and characters from Disney, Pixar, Marvel and Star Wars to create high-quality interactive game experiences, across mobile and console platforms, for fans of all ages.
View More













Publishing and Digital Media DCPI’s Publishing and Digital Media business unit includes Disney Publishing Worldwide and an extensive digital media network that spans mobile, video, influencers, short-form content, and micro-content. The business is focused on drawing a new generation into Disney stories and building original content IP and brands, while attracting engaged audiences across publishing and social platforms.
View More












Citizenship 



Being a good corporate citizen is a time-honored tradition at The Walt Disney Company. Through contributions, collaborations with local organizations, in-kind gifts and volunteering, Disney Cast Members help to strengthen communities and brighten the lives of families around the world.










At Disney Consumer Products and Interactive Media, being a good corporate citizen also includes:

Focusing on the environmental stewardship of our products in collaboration with our top licensees through programs like The SmartPackaging Initiative
Promoting healthier lifestyles through Disney’s Healthy Living Commitment
Creating impactful cause marketing initiatives and content that inspire kids and families to join us in creating a brighter tomorrow
Reaching out to community organizations with product donations

 
Learn More

























